Essentially, with the exclusive power to bypass punitive measures such as mutes, bans, and kicks, users wielding this perk hold a significant advantage over their peers.
If you find yourself unable to reach the server's staff through the traditional support ticket system, don't fret - direct messaging a staff member or administrator will make you eligible for this privilege.
And in the rare event that no other means of contact are available, the appeal server can be used as a last resort to access the support you need.
